             We sent a 6-digit confirmation code to <strong style={{ color: 'var(--text-primary)' }}>{form.email}</strong>. Enter it below to activate your account.
           </p>
           <input 
             type="text" 
             value={otpCode} 
             onChange={e => setOtpCode(e.target.value.replace(/\D/g, ''))} 
